Umuganwa '''Louis (soma Ludoviko mu Kirundi) Rwagasore'''

Louis Rwagasore yavutse italiki 10 muri nzero 1932 muntara ya [[Gitega]]. Yavutse hagati y´umwami [[Mwambutsa]] n´umwamikazi [[Thérèse Kanyonga]]. Ahejeje kaminuza 1956 yaciye itahuka iburundi aca shinga umugambwe [[UPRONA]] kugirango agwanye aba biligi.

